comments: Theis (BOS) slightly extends his hand into Dragic's (MIA) side at the end of the drive but the marginal contact does not affect Dragic's ability to make the pass.
Brown (BOS) legally contests the jump shot by Robinson (MIA).
Iguodala's (MIA) arm is retreating backwards into a vertical position when the marginal contact to Tatum's (BOS) arm occurs during his driving shot attempt.
Dragic (MIA) extends his forearm into Theis' (BOS) body and the contact dislodges him during the rebound.
Dragic (MIA) wraps his arm around Tatum (BOS) and places a stayed hand on his back during the screen. The contact affect Tatum's ability to move freely.
Hayward (BOS) and Robinson (MIA) engage in marginal arm to arm contact off ball prior to the two players separating.
Hayward (BOS) makes contact to Robinson's (MIA) left arm during his shooting motion and the contact affects his jump shot attempt.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Crowder (MIA) reaches in and makes contact to the ball during Tatum's (BOS) drive and any ensuing contact to Tatum's arm is incidental.  Tatum is the last player to touch the ball prior to it going OOB.
Correctly called Delay of Game Violation called on Tatum (BOS).
Iguodala (MIA) swipes down and makes clean contact with the ball during Hayward's (BOS) driving shot attempt.
Robinson (MIA) places his forearm against Hayward's (BOS) back but does not dislodge him during the rebound.
Brown (BOS) makes contact with the ball and cleanly dislodges it during Adebayo's (MIA) upward shooting motion on his shot attempt.

Replay review of the foul called on Robinson (MIA) pursuant to a coach's challenge is deemed unsuccessful.  Robinson is moving laterally and does not establish a legal guarding position in Brown's (BOS) path at the time of his gather on the drive to the basket.
All technical fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
Olynyk (MIA) initiates contact to Theis' (BOS) arm during the rebound that affects his ability to gather the loose ball.
Dragic (MIA) receives the pass and takes more than two steps prior to coming to a stop.
Theis (BOS) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Iguodala's (MIA) path and he is firming up when the contact occurs.
Williams III (BOS) commits a take foul on Robinson (MIA).
Williams III (BOS) commits a take foul on Iguodala (MIA).
Williams III (BOS) commits a take foul on Robinson (MIA).
